import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.cos(x1)
    v1 = jnp.multiply(x0, v0)
    v2 = jnp.add(v1, v1)
    v3 = jnp.abs(x0)
    v4 = jnp.exp(v2)
    v5 = jnp.minimum(v4, x0)
